o_description: The National Education Summit Brisbane is a two-day conference where principals, school leaders, and educators from K-12 can join together. It features interactive seminars by experts and thought leaders in the education sector. The event includes innovative conferences, workshops, and seminars, as well as an education-focused free trade expo called The Education Show. Educators can earn professional development hours by attending the event and choose from various symposiums and seminars. The Education Show showcases cutting-edge resources, programs, support services, and technology. Attendees also have the opportunity to attend free seminars delivered by experts.

o_description: "Premier education, training and employment exhibition"The Melbourne Career Expo is the largest and most comprehensive career event in Victoria. This expo encompasses all career opportunities for employment and training in the trades, corporate, and professional sectors. It offers casual, part-time, and full-time employment from entry-level positions to management and skilled professional roles, as well as apprenticeships and qualified trades jobs. Additionally, it provides information on defence, emergency services, government departments, and initiatives. The expo also offers school leaver information from major universities, TAFEs, and training organizations for years 10-12, as well as tertiary graduate positions and internships. The Melbourne Career Expo is free to attend and is a must for all Victorians seeking a successful future.
